  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Men and postmenopausal women

          -  Age 35-65 years

          -  BMI 27- 34 kg/m2

          -  HbA1c &lt;8%

          -  Fasting plasma cholesterol &lt;250 mg/dl

          -  Fasting plasma triglycerides &lt;300 mg/dl

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hypolipidemic drugs

          -  Plasma creatinine &gt;1.7 mg/dl transaminases &gt; 2 norma values

          -  Ischemic heart disease or positive treadmill stress test

          -  High intensity regular physical activity

          -  Any disease or chronic or/and acute condition contraindicating physical
             activity(anaemia, and infectious, neoplastic, neurological and osteoarticular
             diseases).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
